reviews.name: Boye Aluminum Crochet Hook Set, Sizes E,F,G,H,I & J
reviews.reviewText:
Okay so i dont write reviews very often, and never have for walmart. but decided since there are really no reviews that tell how great this product was i should.

These are my first crochet hooks i was going to buy so i did research on the brand and heard boye is one of the best you can get. I ordered these expecting them in 10 days.. i received them in 5 i was extatic!! i started my project that night (actually tonight lol) right when i got after work when i got them.

Now to the review of the product.. i didnt expect that they would come in a package that has different sections for each hook..and i loved that!! i feel like i dont have to get a hook pouch for this set cause its already in there own seperaters. Like i said before it was my first project but they do have a great variety of hooks for a great price. they glide great and i was able to finish a quarter of my project with ease.

I will DEFINITLY be buying boye again and most likely through walmart because shipping was so so so quick..i ordered late saturday night and received it that wednesday, thats 3 business days!!so Awesome!!! I think i am still giddy about it all after 5 hours :)))
reviews.title: First Set...Amazing Value
